profile:
WHY SHOULD I SEAL MY DRIVEWAY?

Your asphalt driveway or parking lot is exposed to harsh weather conditions everyday without any means of coverage. Sealing and restoring your asphalt with our OIL base sealent (commercial grade) helps  your investment to not :



CRACK due to the strong uv rays , heat and hummidity.



WATER SEEPAGE from heavy rain seeping through cracks causing the driveway foundation to shift.



DAILY WEAR AND TEAR from weight from cars and trucks, oil spills and other leaks, dirt, dust, weeds.



All these threats to your asphalt will cause 

*Chipping and cracking

*Discolouration

*Depressions and potholes

*Compromising the foundation underneath

*Weed growth in cracks due to trapped seeds

OUR SERVICES INCLUDE

* Sealing commercial and residential asphalt driveways and parking lots with oilbase sealer

* Sealing cracks with our commercial grade crack sealer

* Curing oil stains

* Filling GARAGE LIPS

* Filling cracks and potholes

* Taking out weeds from the perimeter of driveway aswell as in cracks.
